EXAMPLE OF WHAT HAS WORKED:

\
They told you to tuck in your shirt to look polished but thats terrible
advice if you have a tummy.Let\'s be honest: High-waisted jeans? They
roll down. Belted dresses? They highlight exactly what you wanted to
hide. So you wear long, flowy tops. You avoid bodycon anything. You
layer to \'create balance.\' But you still feel bulky. Like nothing
flatters you.Here\'s the science: If you\'re apple-shaped with a heavier
midsection---empire cuts and A-line silhouettes skim your stomach
without adding volume.. If you\'re rectangle-shaped---structured jackets
and vertical panels create a waist without cinching. Pair that with
darker tones in your undertone palette? You look streamlined. Not
stuffed. We styled Kavita---a marketing manager from Hyderabad. She
avoided fitted anything. We gave her 16 looks. Peplum tops. Straight
kurtas. Structured co-ords.. She stopped hiding. Started showing up\...
₹999 . 10 slots left this week. Link below.. Book a transformation
now\...